R., Residence\" \u2014 record #49624\nCouncil District: 3\nNeighborhood:     Hosford-Abernethy\nLast sale:        2025-08-04, $1,000,000\nPermit count:     6 (4 final, 2 void)\nLUR cases:        None\nCode enforcement: None visible\nSewer:            Combined sewer; quarter section 3231\nHistoric Plumbing: Available on PortlandMaps for QS 3231/3232\n```\n\n---\n\n*Compiled May 5, 2026. Verify all citations against current code at portland.gov/code; PCC titles are updated frequently and sub-sections renumber. The PP&D website is at portland.gov/ppd. The records request portal is portlandor.govqa.us.*",
